### ðŸ” Interview Tip:

> Method scope avoids naming conflicts and improves memory efficiency.
> 

| Term | Meaning |
| --- | --- |
| Method Scope | Variable inside a method |
| Local Variable | Another name for method-scoped variable |
| Lifetime | During method execution only |

